":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"47141dcadd5118155ed100ed12453ee5c5f674b3","tid":1795384,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:58:21.000Z","msg":"埋下種子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港獨立 唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"獨立完咪又係好似台灣咁有兩岸問題<br />\n唯一出路應該攻打北京<br />\n港獨<br />\n講完都覺得好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7feedc661c83901058c17b3cec0bd55b2f4af7","tid":1795384,"uid":327462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"咁又點<br />\n連登最新風向係落街嗌港獨<br />\n你唔跟就係鬼係5毛係泛民打手"}]}